channel.title: Changing what text says under skull?
channel.description:
Hey everyone, This is totally pathetic, but I forgot how to change what the text under the skull says.
Ex. Skull Here Wild
I want it to say when I'm at Varrock Bank,
Skull Here Safe
But changes once you get into the wild, I just totally forgot how, I'm such a Dumbarse :D.
Thanks, Sebo
